{"tid":1688953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反國歌法, 唔反送中, 叫咩絲","createTime":"2019-11-02T15:36:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T15:54:27.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"25d24329d6618ed9b72249b688a5e7bb6e2b132a","tid":1688953,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T15:36:25.000Z","msg":"送中條例係雙刃劍, 同監控燈柱一樣<br />\n既侵害人權, 但又某程度上對人權又係保障.<br />\n如果你公司迫你上深圳, 不幸遇上變態殺人港犯, 送中都算係保障條友唔會逍遙法外<br />\n<br />\n而國歌法就百分百侵害人權, 對人權零保障<br />\n<br />\n國歌法只係純粹強迫人民愛國和尊重國歌<br />\n沒有給港人任何好處<br />\n<br />\n但反而好多人唔理國歌法"},{"pid":"5af2cec60016131da8bdbdada64db939aebfa4d9","tid":1688953,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T15:37:48.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">入 /task3</span></span><br />\n燒背 候選人被捕 消防員被警察毆打<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5ROL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=f92b9baf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a>"},{"pid":"862e4bb5de91fc04e1e2a245c510b84ea0b7f50e","tid":1688953,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T15:51:24.000Z","msg":"反送中叫黃絲<br />\n反國歌法<br />\n爭取普選叫黃絲<br />\n<br />\n撐送中叫藍絲<br />\n撐國歌法叫藍絲<br />\n撑23叫藍絲<br />\n<br />\n咁如果係<br />\n唔反送中, 甚至部分支持送中, 但撐爭取普選，反國歌法, 反基本法23條，叫咩絲 ?"},{"pid":"11f9f395bc3a89afa3a02b100995f224e55a7352","tid":1688953,"uid":44865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T15:54:27.000Z","msg":"冇腦港豬"}]}